        "\n",
        "\n",
        "First and the foremost, Let us have a bird's eye view of what we can expect in the Online Assessments.\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "*   **General Aptitude** - topics like Speed and Distance , Time and work etc.\n",
        "*   **Technical Aptitude** - All CS fundementals(Os,Cn,DBMS,DSA etc)\n",
